doctype html
html(lang="vi")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title #{pagetitle}
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@latest/tabler-icons.min.css")
    style.
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background: #f5f5f3;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .page-404 {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid #e8e8e6;
        max-width: 480px;
        width: 90%;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .page-404::before,
      .page-404::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 50%;
        pointer-events: none;
        opacity: 0.07;
        filter: blur(60px);
      }

      .page-404::before {
        width: 280px;
        height: 280px;
        background: #534AB7;
        top: -80px;
        right: -60px;
      }

      .page-404::after {
        width: 240px;
        height: 240px;
        background: #1D9E75;
        bottom: -60px;
        left: -40px;
      }

      .icon-wrap {
        width: 72px;
        height: 72px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #f5f4fe;
        border: 1px solid #e0ddfb;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .icon-wrap .ti {
        font-size: 32px;
        color: #534AB7;
      }

      .error-code {
        font-size: 96px;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #534AB7, #1D9E75);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .divider-line {
        width: 48px;
        height: 3px;
        border-radius: 99px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #534AB7, #1D9E75);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .error-title {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .error-desc {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #6b6b6b;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 340px;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .btn-home {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 10px 24px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #534AB7;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: opacity 0.15s, transform 0.1s;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .btn-home:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
      .btn-home:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
      .btn-home .ti { font-size: 16px; }

  body
    .page-404
      .icon-wrap
        i.ti.ti-map-search(aria-hidden="true")

      h1.error-code 404
      .divider-line

      h2.error-title Trang không tìm thấy
      p.error-desc
        | Rất tiếc, trang bạn đang tìm kiếm không tồn tại hoặc đã bị xóa.
        br
        | Vui lòng kiểm tra lại đường dẫn.

      a.btn-home(href="/")
        i.ti.ti-home(aria-hidden="true")
        | Quay lại trang chủ
